<p>...to get the most out of KFormula you need to install 
elsevier's Esstix fonts. You can find them at
<a href="ftp://ftp.elsevier.nl/pub/styles/esstix/esstix.zip">ftp://ftp.elsevier.nl/pub/styles/esstix/esstix.zip</a>.
